Package: CHiMiC
Type: Package
Title: Causal-Guided High-Dimensional Mixed Clustering
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Rui", family = "Ren", email = "ruiren420@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Xiaofeng", family = "Wang", role = "aut"),
    person(given = "Deborah H", family = "Kwon", role = "aut")
  )
Maintainer: Rui Ren <ruiren420@gmail.com>
Description: A statistical method for causal-guided clustering to identify disease phenotypes driven by heterogeneous treatment effects. The method performs clustering on mixed-type clinical data, including continuous and categorical variables, with guidance from heterogeneous treatment effects. A penalty-based variable selection procedure is also implemented to identify relevant clinical variables associated with the discovered clusters.
